== 驅動程式 ==
=== 與UNIX有關的作業系統 ===

[[ATI|ATI]]沒有為基於[[BSD|BSD]]的作業系統推出過任何驅動程式，但就為執行在[[Linux|Linux]]中的[[X_Window_System|X Window System]]提供驅動程式。而基於PowerPC和[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]作業系統的[[Mac_mini|Mac mini]]和[[IBook|iBook G4]]就採用了Radeon 9200顯示卡。

一些Linux用家社區的分支，which prefer to avoid the [[Intellectual_property|IP]]-encumbered ATI drivers due to stability and long term maintainability reasons, still prefer the R200-based chips, as they are among the fastest modern video cards with stable [[open_source_software|open source]] drivers.

=== Windows驅動程式 ===
ATI的[[Catalyst_Drivers|Catalyst Drivers]]支援所有R200以上的Radeon顯示卡，除了[[Windows_XP_Professional_x64_Edition|Windows XP x64]]，直至Catalyst 6.6推出。ATI亦提供舊有驅動程式，Catalyst 6.11則支援9250以下的Radeon顯示卡。

